<div contenteditable="true" class="text-editor"># Welcome to Notepad

## This is a sample document.

• You can write notes here
• Format text using the toolbar
• Save your work for later

Current Time: 3:45 PM
Date: 2023-10-27

Remember to save your work regularly!
